Introduction


Lucky Girls (Korean: 럭키걸스) was a trio under O Entertainment consisting of Sandy, LeeSol, and Harin. They debuted on July 25, 2016 with their digital single Only You (너 하나만) but were a short-lived group as they disbanded later that year.
